#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.27:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Puggalavagga"
msgstr "3. Persons"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Jigucchitabbasutta"
msgstr "27. Offensive"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.27:1.1"
msgid "“Tayome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "“These three people are found in the world."

msgctxt "an3.27:1.2"
msgid "Katame tayo?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.27:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atthi, bhikkhave, puggalo jigucchitabbo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na "
"payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr ""
"There is a person who you should be disgusted by, and you shouldn’t "
"associate with, accompany, or attend them."

msgctxt "an3.27:1.4"
msgid ""
"Atthi, bhikkhave, puggalo ajjhupekkhitabbo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na "
"payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr ""
"There is a person you should regard with equanimity, and you shouldn’t "
"associate with, accompany, or attend them."

msgctxt "an3.27:1.5"
msgid "Atthi, bhikkhave, puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr "There is a person you should associate with, accompany, and attend."

msgctxt "an3.27:1.6"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo jigucchitabbo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na "
"payirupāsitabbo?"
msgstr ""
"Who is the person you should be disgusted by, and not associate with, "
"accompany, or attend?"

msgctxt "an3.27:1.7"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo dussīlo hoti pāpadhammo asuci "
"saṅkassarasamācāro paṭicchannakammanto, assamaṇo samaṇapaṭiñño, abrahmacārī "
"brahmacāripaṭiñño, antopūti avassuto kasambujāto."
msgstr ""
"It’s a person who is unethical, of bad qualities, filthy, with suspicious "
"behavior, underhand, no true ascetic or spiritual practitioner—though "
"claiming to be one—rotten inside, corrupt, and depraved."

msgctxt "an3.27:1.8"
msgid ""
"Evarūpo, bhikkhave, puggalo jigucchitabbo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na "
"payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr ""
"You should be disgusted by such a person, and you shouldn’t associate with, "
"accompany, or attend them."

msgctxt "an3.27:1.9"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an3.27:1.10"
msgid ""
"Kiñcāpi, bhikkhave, evarūpassa puggalassa na diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjati, atha "
"kho naṃ pāpako kittisaddo abbhuggacchati:"
msgstr ""
"Even if you don’t follow the example of such a person, you still get a bad "
"reputation:"

msgctxt "an3.27:1.11"
msgid "‘pāpamitto purisapuggalo pāpasahāyo pāpasampavaṅko’ti."
msgstr "‘That individual has bad friends, companions, and associates.’"

#. VAR: daṃsati → ḍaṃsati (s1-3) | ḍassati (pts1)
msgctxt "an3.27:1.12"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, ahi gūthagato kiñcāpi na daṃsati, atha kho naṃ "
"makkheti;"
msgstr ""
"They’re like a snake that’s been living in a pile of dung. Even if it doesn’"
"t bite, it’ll still rub off on you."

msgctxt "an3.27:1.13"
msgid ""
"evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, kiñcāpi evarūpassa puggalassa na diṭṭhānugatiṃ "
"āpajjati, atha kho naṃ pāpako kittisaddo abbhuggacchati:"
msgstr ""
"In the same way, even if you don’t follow the example of such a person, you "
"still get a bad reputation:"

msgctxt "an3.27:1.14"
msgid "‘pāpamitto purisapuggalo pāpasahāyo pāpasampavaṅko’ti."
msgstr "‘That individual has bad friends, companions, and associates.’"

msgctxt "an3.27:1.15"
msgid ""
"Tasmā evarūpo puggalo jigucchitabbo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na "
"payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr ""
"That’s why you should be disgusted by such a person, and you shouldn’t "
"associate with, accompany, or attend them."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.127"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.27:2.1"
msgid ""
"Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo ajjhupekkhitabbo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na "
"payirupāsitabbo?"
msgstr ""
"Who is the person you should regard with equanimity, and not associate with, "
"accompany, or attend?"

msgctxt "an3.27:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo kodhano hoti upāyāsabahulo, "
msgstr "It’s a person who is irritable and bad-tempered. "

msgctxt "an3.27:2.3"
msgid ""
"appampi vutto samāno abhisajjati kuppati byāpajjati patitthīyati, kopañca "
"dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti."
msgstr ""
"Even when lightly criticized they lose their temper, becoming annoyed, "
"hostile, and hard-hearted, and they display annoyance, hate, and bitterness."

#. VAR: duṭṭhāruko → duṭṭhārukā (bj)
#. VAR: kaṭhalāya → kaṭhalena (bj)
#. VAR: ghaṭṭito → ghaṭṭitā (bj)
#. VAR: āsavaṃ deti → assandati (bj)
msgctxt "an3.27:2.4"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, duṭṭhāruko kaṭṭhena vā kaṭhalāya vā ghaṭṭito bhiyyoso "
"mattāya āsavaṃ deti;"
msgstr ""
"They’re like a festering sore, which, when you hit it with a stick or a "
"stone, discharges even more."

msgctxt "an3.27:2.5"
msgid "evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr "In the same way, someone is prone to anger … and bitterness."

msgctxt "an3.27:2.6"
msgid ""
"seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, tindukālātaṃ kaṭṭhena vā kaṭhalāya vā ghaṭṭitaṃ "
"bhiyyoso mattāya cicciṭāyati ciṭiciṭāyati;"
msgstr ""
"They’re like a firebrand of pale-moon ebony, which, when you hit it with a "
"stick or a stone, sizzles and crackles even more."

msgctxt "an3.27:2.7"
msgid "evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave … pe …"
msgstr "In the same way, someone is prone to anger … and bitterness."

msgctxt "an3.27:2.8"
msgid ""
"seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gūthakūpo kaṭṭhena vā kaṭhalāya vā ghaṭṭito bhiyyoso "
"mattāya duggandho hoti;"
msgstr ""
"They’re like a sewer, which, when you stir it with a stick or a stone, "
"stinks even more."

msgctxt "an3.27:2.9"
msgid "evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, idhekacco puggalo kodhano hoti upāyāsabahulo, "
msgstr "In the same way, someone is irritable and bad-tempered. "

msgctxt "an3.27:2.10"
msgid ""
"appampi vutto samāno abhisajjati kuppati byāpajjati patitthīyati, kopañca "
"dosañca appaccayañca pātukaroti."
msgstr ""
"Even when lightly criticized they lose their temper, becoming annoyed, "
"hostile, and hard-hearted, and they display annoyance, hate, and bitterness."

msgctxt "an3.27:2.11"
msgid ""
"Evarūpo, bhikkhave, puggalo ajjhupekkhitabbo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na "
"payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr ""
"You should regard such a person with equanimity, and you shouldn’t associate "
"with, accompany, or attend them."

msgctxt "an3.27:2.12"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an3.27:2.13"
msgid "Akkoseyyapi maṃ paribhāseyyapi maṃ anatthampi maṃ kareyyāti."
msgstr "Thinking, ‘They might abuse or insult me, or do me harm.’"

msgctxt "an3.27:2.14"
msgid ""
"Tasmā evarūpo puggalo ajjhupekkhitabbo na sevitabbo na bhajitabbo na "
"payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr ""
"That’s why you should regard such a person with equanimity, and you shouldn’"
"t associate with, accompany, or attend them."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.27:3.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo?"
msgstr "Who is the person you should associate with, accompany, and attend?"

msgctxt "an3.27:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo sīlavā hoti kalyāṇadhammo."
msgstr "It’s someone who is ethical, of good character."

msgctxt "an3.27:3.3"
msgid "Evarūpo, bhikkhave, puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr "You should associate with, accompany, and attend such a person."

msgctxt "an3.27:3.4"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "an3.27:3.5"
msgid ""
"Kiñcāpi, bhikkhave, evarūpassa puggalassa na diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjati, atha "
"kho naṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggacchati:"
msgstr ""
"Even if you don’t follow the example of such a person, you still get a good "
"reputation:"

msgctxt "an3.27:3.6"
msgid "‘kalyāṇamitto purisapuggalo kalyāṇasahāyo kalyāṇasampavaṅko’ti."
msgstr "‘That individual has good friends, companions, and associates.’"

msgctxt "an3.27:3.7"
msgid "Tasmā evarūpo puggalo sevitabbo bhajitabbo payirupāsitabbo."
msgstr ""
"That’s why you should associate with, accompany, and attend such a person."

msgctxt "an3.27:3.8"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, tayo puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasminti."
msgstr "These are the three people found in the world.”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an3.27:4.1"
msgid "Nihīyati puriso nihīnasevī,"
msgstr "“A man who associates with an inferior goes downhill,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.27:4.2"
msgid "Na ca hāyetha kadāci tulyasevī;"
msgstr "But associating with an equal, you’ll never decline;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.27:4.3"
msgid "Seṭṭhamupanamaṃ udeti khippaṃ,"
msgstr "Following the best, you’ll quickly rise up,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.27:4.4"
msgid "Tasmā attano uttariṃ bhajethā”ti."
msgstr "So you should keep company with people better than you.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.27:4.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
